sentences: Christopher Simms Jr. (born February 6, 1998), known by his stage name Cico P (formerly "Cicoeee P"), is an American rapper, singer, and songwriter.
Cico P hails from Jacksonville, Texas.
His recent single, "Tampa" has achieved viral popularity on TikTok in early 2021.
"Tampa" catapulted Cico P to the top of the US Spotify Viral 50 chart as well as the #3 spot on Rolling Stone’s Breakthrough 25 and #41 on Billboard’s Emerging Artists.
